Detailed Description

cvmx_ocla::_fsm::_and::_i#

Values for PLA-AND plane. AND(0..15) represents the 16 allowed AND terms. I(0..1) for I=0 indicates the term non-inverted, for I=1 indicates the term inverted. Any AND tree may be disabled by setting the same bit in both _I(0) and _I(1), as '((1) & !(1))' is always false.
